:10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"711c2452b0","type":"paragraph","text":"暴君用刀剑和棍棒审判我们， 因为他怕自由象怕火一样；","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"e355fb98f7","type":"paragraph","text":"他害怕一旦我们找到了自由， 他的宝座就会摇晃，他就要遭殃！","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"2df830a26a","type":"paragraph","text":"昂起头来啊！兄弟们用不着懊丧，囚禁、迫害、侮辱……那又有何妨？","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"d3d89bab64","type":"paragraph","text":"我们是殉道者，光荣的囚犯， 这镣链是我们骄傲的勋章。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"7fd76014d4","type":"paragraph","text":"*          *          *","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"12d57b1294","type":"paragraph","text":"一个苍白的青年倚着桅樯，   仿佛已支不住镣链的重量，","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"fb48a6b60b","type":"paragraph","text":"他动也不动象一尊塑像，     只有眼睛星星般在发亮。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"ff474e04e1","type":"paragraph","text":"梦想什么呢？年轻的伙伴！   是想着千百里外的家乡？","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"46017cb213","type":"paragraph","text":"是想着白发飘萧的老母？     是想着温柔情重的姑娘？","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"4f54ee7850","type":"paragraph","text":"别再想了吧！别再去多想，   一切都已被剥夺得精光。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"668014c21e","type":"paragraph","text":"我们没有未来，我们没有幻想，甚至不知道明天见不见太阳。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"1b9960f9af","type":"paragraph","text":"荒凉的海岛，阴暗的牢房，   一小时比一年更加漫长，","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"7808d01648","type":"paragraph","text":"活着，锁链伴了呼吸的节奏起落，死去，也还要带着镣铐一起埋葬。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"036b26eeff","type":"paragraph","text":"*          *          *","index":24,"publication