":"2180fca5f4","type":"paragraph","text":"象幼儿的乳母唤叫孩子，     象离母的婴孩索要亲娘。","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"436176fc58","type":"paragraph","text":"我宁愿被放逐到穷山僻野，   我宁愿在天幔下四处流浪，","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"4ec1ece9e4","type":"paragraph","text":"宁愿去住在狐狸的洞里，     把清风当被，黄土当床。","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"01d1991105","type":"paragraph","text":"宁愿去检掘松子和野菜，     跟飞鸟们吃一样的食粮，","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"2209532575","type":"paragraph","text":"我宁愿牺牲一切甚至生命，   只要自由这瓌宝在我身旁，","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"d63176bb54","type":"paragraph","text":"我宁愿让满腔沸腾的鲜血，   洒上那冰冷的枯瘠的土地，","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"6e206d6dde","type":"paragraph","text":"宁愿把前途、爱情、幸福、   一起抛向这无限的波浪。","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"a224bc7782","type":"paragraph","text":"只要我的血象沥青一样，     铺平自由来到人间的道路，","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"95f7f1fe37","type":"paragraph","text":"我不惜把一切能够献出的东西，完完全全地献作她自由的拉羊。","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"e3a9535fcc","type":"paragraph","text":"多少世纪，多少年代啊，自由！人们追寻你像黑夜里追求太阳，","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"9ece81ceed","type":"paragraph","text":"父亲在屠刀的闪光里微笑倒下，儿子又默默地承继父亲的希望，","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"1430d5635d","type":"paragraph","text":"钢刀已经被牺牲者的筋骨磕钝，铁锈也已经被囚徒们的皮肉磨光。","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"f95ab89acd","type":"paragraph","text":"多难的土地啊，浸润着血泪，山般高的白骨砌堆成狱墙，","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"d7db8792ee","type":"paragraph","text":"埋葬的坟墓里多少死尸张着两眼，为的是没能看见你，自由的曙光。","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"bac