dd","type":"paragraph","text":"远远地出现了一个黑点，     年青人睁大眼对它凝望，","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"71a0aba020","type":"paragraph","text":"听见谁轻声说：是一个岛，   他的心便猛然撞击胸膛。","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"f9098cb787","type":"paragraph","text":"海岛啊！你是个什么地方，   也许你不过是海鸥的栈房，","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"5999afdd01","type":"paragraph","text":"也许你荒僻没有人迹，       也许你常淹没在海的波浪。","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"b1705586b3","type":"paragraph","text":"但是这一切又算得什么？     只要你没有禁锢自由的狱墙，","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"2b0c179b29","type":"paragraph","text":"只要你没有束缚心灵的枷锁， 对于我来说你就是天堂。","index":72,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"817d85bad7","type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢的黑眼睛燃烧着光芒，   他走前一步（镣链叮当作响），","index":73,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"d545cb41b0","type":"paragraph","text":"暗暗地目测着水上的距离，   对自由的渴望给了他力量。","index":74,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"77baa13ed6","type":"paragraph","text":"我能够游过去么？能还是不？ 也许押送者的枪弹会把我追上，","index":75,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"8341418c56","type":"paragraph","text":"也许沉重的镣链会把我拖下水底，也许大海的波浪会叫我身丧海浪，","index":76,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"a2e4ad0c66","type":"paragraph","text":"我能游到那里么？能还是不？ 我要试一试——不管会怎么样！","index":77,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"58115c91fd","type":"paragraph","text":"宁可做逃犯葬身在海底，     也强似在囚禁中憔悴地死亡。","index":78,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"b24513311a","type":"paragraph","text":"不管付出什么代价，在我死去之前，也得要吸一口自由的空气，","index":79,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"c81e4b2c0d","type":"paragraph","text":"即使我有卅次生命的权利，   我也只有会都献到神圣的自由祭坛上。","index":80,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"9609512660","type":"paragraph","text":"别了，乡土和母亲！别了，爱我的你！我的祝福将长和你们依旁。","index":81,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"3593dab20e","type":"paragraph","text":"别了，失败的战友！别了，不屈的伙伴！你们是多么英勇又多么善良，","index":82,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"2d1e4203d1","type":"paragraph","text":"可惜我只能用眼睛和心拥抱你们，   愿你们死得高傲死得坚强！","index":83,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"191ba80ddf","type":"paragraph","text":"别了，谁知道也许这就是永别，     但是我没法——为了追踪我们的理想，","index":84,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"2f370a927e","type":"appellation","text":"啊！自由，宇宙间最最贵重的名字， 只要找到你，我们的一切牺牲，","index":85,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"4cceef9265","type":"appellation","text":"便都获得了光荣的补偿……","index":86,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"c2b3ad2482","type":"paragraph","text":"*          *          *","index":87,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"7e2b87cb91","type":"paragraph","text":"他握紧双拳一声响亮， 迸断的镣铐落在甲板上，","index":88,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"7fd4cb25da","type":"paragraph","text":"他象飞燕般纵到栏边， 深深吸口气投进了海洋。","index":89,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"60d25f0696","type":"paragraph","text":"枪弹追赶着他的行程， 波浪也捲着他死死不放，","index":90,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"c65973eec7","type":"paragraph","text":"那个黑点却还是那么遥远…… 他只是奋力地泅向前方。","index":91,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"7642fda443","type":"paragraph","text":"海风啊！为什么兴啸狂号？   海浪啊！为什么这样激荡？","index":92,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"bcecd9b1fe","type":"paragraph","text":"臂膊象灌了铅那么沉重，     年青的逃犯用尽了力量。","index":93,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"2685fdb4c2","type":"paragraph","text":"最后一次努力浮上水面，     把自由的空气吸满了肺脏，","index":94,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"e73d9f56e3","type":"paragraph","text":"马上，一个大浪吞没了他，   从此他再没能游出水上。","index":95,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"d680dc33a4","type":"paragraph","text":"押送者停止了活靶射击，     追捕的小艇也收起双桨，","index":96,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"d91cea7d9f","type":"paragraph","text":"难友们化石般凝视水面，     无声地哀悼壮烈的死亡。","index":97,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"fb9262917c","type":"paragraph","text":"……年青的伙伴，我们的兄弟，难道你已经真葬身海洋？","index":98,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"ef0655d08e","type":"paragraph","text":"难道我们再听不见你激情爽朗的声音？再看不见你坚定果决的面庞？","index":99,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"db0c0ffc06","type":"paragraph","text":"难道我们再不能和你在一起战斗？为争取自由的理想献出力量？","index":100,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"79c1edfc4a","type":"paragraph","text":"海浪啊！那么高那么凉，     我们的心却象火炭一样！","index":101,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"6278cb2cdf","type":"paragraph","text":"听啊！我们年青的兄弟，     悲壮的輓歌发自我们的心房，","index":102,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"57e2caaef1","type":"paragraph","text":"记得你，无畏的英烈的形象， 记得你，为自由献身的榜样！","index":103,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"f36f7a929c","type":"paragraph","text":"记得你啊！我们最最勇敢的战士，在一场力量悬殊的战斗中，","index":104,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"ffb27d9ab0","type":"paragraph","text":"你从容自若地迎接了死亡，   海浪啊，请抚慰我们年青的兄弟，","index":105,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"0cac39dc32","type":"paragraph","text":"海风啊，把我们的輓歌散到四方，象春风带着万千颗种子，","index":106,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"fe4d01b603","type":"paragraph","text":"散向万千颗爱自由的心房……","index":107,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"2c824df6c0","type":"paragraph","text":"*          *          *","index":108,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"b339b2742b","type":"paragraph","text":"那是什么——囚人们且莫悲伤，看啊！就在年青人沉没的地方，","index":109,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"6aa19df8fb","type":"paragraph","text":"一只雪白的海鸥飞出了波浪， 展开宽阔的翅膀冲风翱翔。","index":110,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"5aab0b9599","type":"paragraph","text":"这是他，我们不屈的斗士，   他冲进死亡去战胜了死亡，","index":111,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"a00e239ad3","type":"paragraph","text":"残留的锁链已沉埋在海底，   如今啊，他自由得象风一样。","index":112,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"58326e754f","type":"paragraph","text":"啊！海鸥！啊！英勇的叛徒， 他将在死者中蒙受荣光，","index":113,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"3e68a6da19","type":"paragraph","text":"他的灵魂已经化为自由——   万里晴空下到处是家乡！","index":114,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"},{"id":"8acee6cbc5","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：谭蝉雪编著《求索（兰州大学“右派反革命集团案”纪实）》，2010年。","index":115,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf"}],"page":{"id":"fc15345939","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"31e2f35bbf","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}